{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services/about","content_id":"3114e256-f2e1-49bb-9357-6ac66dd4e544","description":"We are the single front door for international financial services firms wishing to set up or expand their operations in the UK. We provide regulatory assistance and wider business support to ensure a streamlined investor experience. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services\">Office for Investment: Financial Services (<abbr title=\"Office for Investment: Financial Services\">OfI:FS</abbr>)</a> is a dedicated concierge service within the Office for Investment.</p>\n\n<p>By bringing together the different elements of the UK ecosystem, including the regulatory bodies, the <abbr title=\"Office for Investment: Financial Services\">OfI:FS</abbr> offers comprehensive and bespoke support in a structured, co-ordinated way to firms looking to establish and expand their presence in the UK.</p>\n\n<p>Our team of financial services experts operates in partnership with:  </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-treasury\"><abbr title=\"His Majesty's\">HM</abbr> Treasury</a> </li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.fca.org.uk/firms/support-services\">Financial Conduct Authority</a> </li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/prudential-regulation/authorisations/new-firm-authorisation\">Prudential Regulation Authority</a> </li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.theglobalcity.uk/OFI-Financial-Services\">City of London Corporation</a> </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We are focused on increasing the attractiveness of the UK’s financial services sector and supporting firms in navigating the regulatory landscape. This supports the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-investment\">Office for Investment’s</a> wider objectives of securing investment that drives growth, job creation and increased productivity across the UK.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Details added about the work of the Office for Investment: Financial Services. Links to the Financial Conduct Authority, Prudential Regulation Authority and City of London Corporation updated.","public_timestamp":"2025-10-17T08:00:02Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2025-07-15T08:00:01Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[],"organisation":"b050b584-ccea-4dab-9755-da463f601917","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2025-07-15T09:00:01+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services/about","content_id":"3114e256-f2e1-49bb-9357-6ac66dd4e544","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-17T08:00:02Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services/about","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1449","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services","content_id":"b050b584-ccea-4dab-9755-da463f601917","details":{"acronym":"OfI:FS","brand":"department-for-business-trade","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Office for Investment: Financial Services"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}}